<p><strong>Features</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>View friend states, are they online and in-game</li>
<li>Chat with friends</li>
<li>Alerts when receiving a chat message</li>
</ul>
<div><strong>Technology</strong></div>
<div> </div>
<div>Mono for Android</div>
<div> </div>
<div><strong>Description</strong></div>
<p>Steam Droid is free and available on the <a href="https://market.android.com/details?id=com.flyingpie.steamdroid">Android Market</a>, you can simply enter the credentials of your Steam account and you're ready to go!</p>
<p>Please feel free do leave any comments or features requests at the forums at <a href="http://www.facepunch.com/threads/1151619">Facepunch</a>, or send me a mail at marco [at] flyingpie [dot] nl.</p>
<p>Steam Droid is open source and can be downloaded from <a href="https://github.com/FlyingPie/SteamDroid">GitHub</a>.</p>
<p><em>Unfortunately, SteamDroid has been removed from the Android Market, but the project is still available from GitHub.</em></p>
